text: Koo! Ulia wachaka okhumbakha eshiumbashe shishie khulwe lichomo liokhuria Nyasaye nende okhwenya obuchami bubwe ni omulayi nohomba ulia owachaka okhumbakha eshiumbashe shishie khulichomo lie eshiumbashe shishie hekulu khundulo welitukho weliloba lialo lilakakhanga, mana nakwa nashio mumulilo kwa Jahannam, ne Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu ababii tawe
